title: London Estate Agent Dexters Owner Exploring Potential Sale: Sky
description: Private equity firm Oakley Capital is exploring a potential sale of London’s biggest estate agency chain that could value it at more than £500 million ($673 million), Sky News reported on Saturday, citing sources it didn’t name.
